cdata.name: Ripio
cdata.desc: RCN is a global credit network based on cosigned smart contracts that connects lenders and borrowers located anywhere in the world and on any currency. The smart contracts connect agents with information on the borrowers identity to agents that analyze the borrowers credit risk impartially, thus standardizing credit lending through blockchain technology. A cosigner acts as a re insurer that distributes and reduces the lenders risk and, at the same time, helps to improve the contract conditions by retaining access to the borrowers local legal system.
